sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Pengguna
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant AG as Agentic Pipeline
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant KG as Neo4j

    U->>FE: Menulis pesan
    FE->>GW: Kirim pesan percakapan
    GW->>PG: Simpan pesan pengguna
    GW->>AG: Minta respons agentic
    activate AG
    AG->>AG: Guardrail dan pemahaman konteks
    AG->>PG: Ambil konteks semantik
    AG->>KG: Ambil konteks relasional
    AG->>AG: Pilih strategi respons
    AG-->>GW: Respons dan state percakapan
    deactivate AG
    GW->>PG: Simpan respons asisten
    GW-->>FE: Kembalikan respons
    FE-->>U: Tampilkan balasan
